name: mango smoothie
description:
"mango smoothie" is the 12th and last song off my new beattape "souls" releaseing August 27, 2021. mango smoothie is repetitive, soothing and perfect for a sunday afternoon.  

the cover art was generated by AI using the text prompt "mango smoothie" 

Bop your head and enjoy the music. If you purchase this piece, hit me up on twitter @ryanartwalker and I will send you the album with high quality WAV files!
